  "detailed_description": "<strong>Flipon</strong> is a juicy and fun arcade puzzle game full of surprises!<br><br>Mine flipoblocks by aligning them to make combos, solve puzzles and defeat the (cute) bad guys!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/5d0720d224ad45a5a56cf4cdeb978011.poster.avif?t=1762692839\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/5d0720d224ad45a5a56cf4cdeb978011.webm?t=1762692839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/5d0720d224ad45a5a56cf4cdeb978011.mp4?t=1762692839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><br>Join <strong>Kat</strong> and her crew of flipoblock miners in an epic quest in the Flipon solar system!<br>Embark your ship and visit 75+ differents levels though 5+ planets. But beware, each planet is owned by a powerful guardian and each level is a new challenge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/a2159eae987f63cbd45658da70fb1832.avif?t=1762692839\" width=500 height=470 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> CAMPAIGN: 75+ levels mixing 5 game modes: objectives, survival, boss fights, puzzles and challenges!<br></li><li> SCORE ATTACK: an infinite scoring mode with online leaderboards<br></li><li> CHALLENGE: a procedural puzzle generator<br></li><li> VERSUS: local multiplayer fights, up to 4 players!<br></li><li> POWERS: discover and use wisely 6 different powers during your fights!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Flipon</strong> is a juicy and fun arcade puzzle game full of surprises!<br><br>Mine flipoblocks by aligning them to make combos, solve puzzles and defeat the (cute) bad guys!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/5d0720d224ad45a5a56cf4cdeb978011.poster.avif?t=1762692839\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/5d0720d224ad45a5a56cf4cdeb978011.webm?t=1762692839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/5d0720d224ad45a5a56cf4cdeb978011.mp4?t=1762692839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><br>Join <strong>Kat</strong> and her crew of flipoblock miners in an epic quest in the Flipon solar system!<br>Embark your ship and visit 75+ differents levels though 5+ planets. But beware, each planet is owned by a powerful guardian and each level is a new challenge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285020/extras/a2159eae987f63cbd45658da70fb1832.avif?t=1762692839\" width=500 height=470 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> CAMPAIGN: 75+ levels mixing 5 game modes: objectives, survival, boss fights, puzzles and challenges!<br></li><li> SCORE ATTACK: an infinite scoring mode with online leaderboards<br></li><li> CHALLENGE: a procedural puzzle generator<br></li><li> VERSUS: local multiplayer fights, up to 4 players!<br></li><li> POWERS: discover and use wisely 6 different powers during your fights!</li></ul>",
